      "id": "2028383098451497414",
      "text": "RT @XFreeze: Elon Musk has been planning satellite-to-mobile internet for years and it’s now becoming reality\n\nHigh-bandwidth connectivity…",
      "created_at": "Mon Mar 02 08:13:10 +0000 2026",
      "lang": "en",
      "media": [],
      "retweet": {
        "id": "2028373770663006665",
        "text": "Elon Musk has been planning satellite-to-mobile internet for years and it’s now becoming reality\n\nHigh-bandwidth connectivity directly from Starlink satellites to your regular phone is coming\n\nStarlink has officially announced its next-generation 5G Mobile V2 satellites\n\n“So in parallel, we’re building the satellites and working with the handset makers to add these frequencies to the phones. And then the satellites and the phones will handshake very well to achieve high-bandwidth connectivity\"\n\nElon’s vision:\n“You should be able to watch videos anywhere on your phone”\n\nTrue global coverage with no dead zones - exactly what Elon has been working toward for years",
