      "id": "2028471510298694032",
      "text": "RT @Starlink: Starlink Mobile is partnering with @deutschetelekom to support over 140M subscribers across 10 European countries. \n\nThe serv…",
      "created_at": "Mon Mar 02 14:04:29 +0000 2026",
