      "retweet": {
        "id": "2028459012363309232",
        "text": "Starlink Mobile is partnering with @deutschetelekom to support over 140M subscribers across 10 European countries. \n\nThe service will be the first in the region to launch V2 next-gen technology using our new Mobile Satellite Service spectrum, which will deliver 5G speeds to cell phones in remote areas. → https://t.co/CV6MjKASx7",
