        "lang": "en",
        "media": [],
        "retweet": null,
        "quoted": {
          "id": "2028455278841090193",
          "text": "Starting in 2028, we will complement our mobile network with satellite connectivity from @Starlink. This will allow us to close the very last white spots in Europe - for example inaccessible terrain or protected natural areas.\n\nMore on this: https://t.co/616ULGcuBA https://t.co/9GmBKGyt5w",
